    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Affordable and ready to hit the road! This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's a solid, drivable vehicle that handles daily duties dependably, though it does show some noticeable wear inside and out and may have a few minor mechanical quirks to be aware of. Nothing that should stop you from enjoying it, but worth factoring into your plans. A great pick for a practical buyer looking for reliable transportation without breaking the bank!",
